Hello?

5
00:00:25,542 --> 00:00:28,875
<i>Hi, this is the Kaohsiung General Hospital.</i>

6
00:00:28,875 --> 00:00:33,458
<i>May I ask if this is the emergency contact
of Huang Ping-Xiang and Huang Ping-Wei?</i>

7
00:00:33,458 --> 00:00:37,417
<i>There was a serious car accident.
Currently, they are in the ER room.</i>

8
00:00:37,417 --> 00:00:39,292
<i>Please hurry to the hospital.</i>

9
00:00:39,292 --> 00:00:42,300
<i>It's urgent and they may need surgeries.</i>

10
00:00:54,542 --> 00:00:56,008
What happened?

11
