How's Neil?

12
00:02:16,333 --> 00:02:19,008
He finally fell asleep.

13
00:02:23,167 --> 00:02:25,375
<i>It's my birthday.</i>

14
00:02:25,375 --> 00:02:27,175
<i>No exceptions.</i>

15
00:02:27,175 --> 00:02:30,350
<i>Happy birthday.</i>

16
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:42,720
When are you going back to Thailand?

17
00:02:43,543 --> 00:02:45,552
Next week.

18
